sentences: Fabio Frittelli (24 July 1966 â€“ 6 February 2013), better known by his pseudonym Mo-Do, was an Italian musician.
The name Mo-Do is claimed to originate from first letters of Frittelli's birth town (Monfalcone) and the day of his birth (Domenica, i.e. "Sunday" in Italian), respectively.
Frittelli was found dead at his home in Italy on 7 February 2013, at age 46.
